                         ''The Unbearable Lightness," by Slovakian designer Tomas Libertiny. The work, made with the help of live bees, is an edition of six and was priced at 65,000 euros at the booth of Carpenters Workshop Gallery at the Design Miami/Basel fair in Switzerland. The buyer was Roman Abramovich, according to dealers. 
                       
                     
                                        
           
